ews faq about contracting  usace usace information sheet on rio  statement by alfred v neffgen chief operating officer kbr government operations americas region before the committee on government reform united states house of representatives pdf july   archived from the original pdf on july     james risen june   army overseer tells of ouster over kbr stir the new york times p a   kbr to get nobid army work as us alleges kickbacks business week may    farah stockman top iraq contractor skirts us taxes offshore shell companies in cayman islands allow kbr to avoid medicare social security deductions the boston globe   kbr charged with bribing nigerian officials for contracts cnn   kellogg brown  root llc pleads guilty to foreign bribery charges and agrees to pay  million criminal fine press release department of justice february     september   albert jackson stanley plea agreement usdc southern district of texas houston division  sec charges former ceo of kellogg brown  root inc with foreign bribery   industry experts call halliburton gasoline prices highway robbery committee on oversight and government reform  united states house of representatives october   archived from the original on december     kbr implements plan for extinguishing oil well fires in iraq press release halliburton march   archived from the original on april     risen james  despite alert flawed wiring still kills gis the new york times retrieved    green beret electrocuted in shower on iraq base – cnncom cnn may   retrieved may     iraq electrocutions show us failed to provide for troops standardspeaker hazleton pennsylvania august   archived from the original on april     a b scott bronstein abbie boudreau january   investigator soldiers electrocution negligent homicide cnn   kbr tries to convince judge to use iraqi law in shower death of green beret allgov february     hefling kimberly kbr wins contract despite criminal probe of deaths associated press via abc news   kbr iraq cases involve ca